des: The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. The Ranier Performance Daily Health and Fitness Show serves to educate the public on the latest health topics. We believe your health is a variable you're able to control if armed with the proper tools and resources. Each day Ranier releases a simple tip or fact on how you can better your health and pave the path to a healthier lifestyle. Daily tips cover topics anywhere from how to stretch your hamstrings to how to optimize your health care experience and much more. If it has anything to do with health, we're covering it. Interested in hearing or learning more about a particular topic? Let us know!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
